OL,3,CLeukaemia survivor, 18, now living
OL,4,Cchildhood dream as apprentice binman
OL,6,FDaniel Kinsella, 18, tells Good
OL,7,FMorning Britain's Philip Sime why he
OL,8,Floves being a binman and how happy he
OL,9,Fis to land his dream job after
OL,10,Fovercoming his illness
OL,12,FA teenager from the Wirral has landed
OL,13,Fhis dream job as a bin man, after
OL,14,Fdeveloping a passion for refuse
OL,15,Fcollection while receiving treatment
OL,16,Ffor Leukaemia as a child.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
