OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1780074357
OL,3,CLeukaemia survivor, 18, now living
OL,4,Cchildhood dream as apprentice binman
OL,6,FDaniel Kinsella, 18, from Leasowe, is
OL,7,Fnow working as an apprentice loader
OL,8,Ffor waste collection firm Gaskells,
OL,9,Fand is learning on the job as he works
OL,10,Ftowards his HGV licence.
OL,12,FHis dream of driving bin lorries goes
OL,13,Fback years to when he was a young boy,
OL,14,Fwith his mother Michelle first
OL,15,Fnoticing his interest during a family
OL,16,Fholiday to Australia.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
