PN,31203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1780074357
OL,3,CLeukaemia survivor, 18, now living
OL,4,Cchildhood dream as apprentice binman
OL,6,F"We went on this amazing holiday and
OL,7,Fwe had to follow the bin wagon around
OL,8,Fthe streets of Sydney because Daniel
OL,9,Fwas just obsessed," she told Good
OL,10,FMorning Britain.
OL,12,FWhile undergoing chemotherapy for
OL,13,FLeukaemia, aged six, Kinsella was
OL,14,Finvited to join Gaskells' binmen on
OL,15,Ftheir collections around Crosby in
OL,16,F2014 and was given a VIP tour of the
OL,17,Ffirm's refuse plant.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1780074357
OL,3,CLeukaemia survivor, 18, now living
OL,4,Cchildhood dream as apprentice binman
OL,6,FThe firm named one of its lorries
OL,7,Fafter him, and Kinsella was given a
OL,8,Fchild-sized uniform, which he loved so
OL,9,Fmuch he even wore it while going for
OL,10,Ftests at Alder Hey Children's Hospital.
OL,12,FKinsella went on to beat cancer, and
OL,13,Fhis love of waste collection showed no
OL,14,Fsign of dying as he grew older, paying
OL,15,FGaskells another visit around four
OL,16,Fyears later.
OL,18,FNow aged 18, he started his new job
OL,19,Fwith Gaskells in May and is loving
OL,20,Fevery moment.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
