PN,31205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1780074357
OL,3,CLeukaemia survivor, 18, now living
OL,4,Cchildhood dream as apprentice binman
OL,6,FAsked if he's had any unpleasant
OL,7,Fsurprises in his first few weeks on
OL,8,Fthe job, he told GMB: "Not really `
OL,9,Fjust a few rats jumping out."
OL,11,FExplaining why he loves the job so
OL,12,Fmuch, he said: "I just like being
OL,13,Foutdoors more than your typical office
OL,14,Fjob.
OL,16,F"I like the fact that you get to meet
OL,17,Fyour customers, you get to socialise
OL,18,Fwith them and speak to them.
OL,20,F"And you go there every week so you
OL,21,Fget a real connection with them."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1780074357
OL,3,CLeukaemia survivor, 18, now living
OL,4,Cchildhood dream as apprentice binman
OL,6,F"It's great to finally be here," he
OL,7,Fadded. "Getting through my illness and
OL,8,Fthen being able to do what I've wanted
OL,9,Fto do from when I was so young as a
OL,10,Ffull-time career."
